cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is about end-to-end speech recognition using a modified LSTM-CTC model. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and speech recognition. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves signal processing techniques, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). Finally, the paper proposes a new model architecture, which could fall under cs.SI (Systems and Control).
